This document lists the changes between stable releases.

The version numbers follow [semantic versioning].

[semantic versioning]: http://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html


## lua‑mpi 0.2 (2015-04-24) {#v0.2}

  * Add datatypes for reduce of maximum/minimum location.
  * Support in-place collective communication.
  * Add Cartesian process topology.
  * Add user-defined datatypes.
  * Support compilation with GCC 5.

Thanks to Lesley De Cruz for contributing to this release.

## lua‑mpi 0.1 (2014-12-01) {#v0.1}

  * Initial release of MPI for Lua.
